description: Gets the price sheet for a scope by subscriptionId. Price sheet is available via this API only for May 1, 2014 or later.

skiptoken.description: Skiptoken is only used if a previous operation returned a partial result. If a previous response contains a nextLink element, the value of the nextLink element will include a skiptoken parameter that specifies a starting point to use for subsequent calls.

api_version.description: Version of the API to be used with the client request. The current version is 2019-05-01.

top.description: May be used to limit the number of results to the top N results.
